String palindrome
Write a program to find whether the given string is a palindrome or not

Input Format

Read a string

Constraints

string

Output Format

If the given string is a Palindrome display “Palindrome”, else display “Not a Palindrome”.

Sample Input 0

madam
Sample Output 0

Palindrome
Sample Input 1

java
Sample Output 1

Not a Palindrome
